### command line
For my mac, since I store my ssh-key under "/Users/mac/ .ssh/id_rsa". would change it to my path
> docker-machine create --driver generic --generic-ip-address=172.31.86.190 --generic-ssh-key "/Users/mac/.ssh/id_rsa" --generic-ssh-user=aiservice remote-docker-host
